lead_paragraph: Santi Cazorla scored a 94th-minute penalty as sub-par Arsenal beat Southampton on Saturday with Laurent Koscielny's overhead kick having earlier cancelled out Petr Cech's own goal.

headline.print_headline: Cazorla Penalty Gives Arsenal Late Win Over Southampton
headline.main: Cazorla Penalty Gives Arsenal Late Win Over Southampton
